Ready-Set-Go Task:

  • First, a red circle ("Ready") appears
  • Then, after a delay, an orange circle ("Set") appears
  • After "Set" disappears, screen goes blank
  • You must press SPACE when you think the same delay has passed
  • After you press, a green circle will appear
  • Then you'll see how close your timing was (only for the first 5 trials).
